Àtụ:Infobox ice hockey player
Sven Leuenberger (amụrụ ya n'abalị iri abụọ na ise n'ọnwa Ọgọstụ n'afọ 1969 na Niederuzwil, Switzerland) ọ bụ onye na-agbachitere ice hockey na Switzerland.
Ọ bụ onye isi njikwa nke ZSC Lions ugbu a.6
N'ịgba bọọlụ na NLA, Leuenberger gbara goolu iri asaa na anọ, nyere aka iri asaa na atọ, na nkeji iri anọ na anọ na oge ahụ.
Leuenberger jere ozi dị ka General Manager maka SC Bern site n'afọ 2006 ruo Disemba afọ 2015
Ọ gara n'ihu na-azụ ndị otu Bern U20 maka oge fọdụrụ n'afọ 2015-16.
N'abalị mbụ n'ọnwa Ọgọstụ n'afọ 2008, onye nkuzi SC Bern, John van Boxmeer, nwere nkụchi obi nke gbara ya gburugburu otu ọnwa
N'oge van Boxmeer na-anọghị ya, General Manager Sven Leuenberger zụrụ ndị otu ahụ ya na onye na-enyere onye nkuzi Konstantin Kurashev aka.
Sven Leuenberger gbara egwuregwu 124 maka ndị otu emba Switzerland.
